278
00:16:21,875 --> 00:16:24,125
Four thousand,
five hundred and twenty.

279
00:16:24,208 --> 00:16:32,625
♪

280
00:16:32,708 --> 00:16:33,916
That light! Oh, no!

281
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,458
Don't, Sissy!

282
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,583
