00:18:38,458 --> 00:18:40,833
[MUSUJIME chuckles] But wait!

309
00:18:40,916 --> 00:18:42,250
Huh?

310
00:18:42,333 --> 00:18:43,625
[MUSUJIME] On August 31st,
you were shot in the head,

311
00:18:43,708 --> 00:18:46,541
which resulted in
the loss of your power.

312
00:18:46,625 --> 00:18:49,125
Yeah, you no longer
have the ability

313
00:18:49,208 --> 00:18:51,375
to calculate
like you did before.

314
00:18:51,458 --> 00:18:54,625
You're washed up! I don't
have to be afraid of you!

315
00:18:55,958 --> 00:18:57,708
Ya know, I feel bad for you.

316
00:18:57,791 --> 00:18:59,958
Really, if you actually
believe what you're saying,

317
00:19:00,041 --> 00:19:03,500
I feel so bad for you I
could almost give you a hug.

318
00:19:03,583 --> 00:19:05,375
It's true that I was
involved in a scuffle

319
00:19:05,458 --> 00:19:07,541
that left me with
some brain damage.

320
00:19:07,625 --> 00:19:10,416
So nowadays I
outsource my calculating.

321
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:11,791
Here's the thing, though...

322
00:19:11,875 --> 00:19:13,958
I may be a bit weaker
because of that,

323
00:19:14,041 --> 00:19:16,833
but it's still a far cry
from being as weak as you are.

324
00:19:16,916 --> 00:19:20,166
You really think I'd
fallen that far? Huh?!

325
00:19:20,541 --> 00:19:32,500
♪

326
00:19:32,583 --> 00:19:34,083
[ACCELERATOR chuckles]

327
00:19:35,625 --> 00:19:36,708
[ACCELERATOR grunts]

328
00:19:38,458 --> 00:19:40,291
[ACCELERATOR] It's all over.
Unless you want me

329
00:19:40,375 --> 00:19:42,125
to accelerate your death,

330
00:19:42,208 --> 00:19:44,416
I suggest you surrender
like a good little girl,

331
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:46,333
go back to wherever
it is you came from,

332
00:19:46,416 --> 00:19:48,125
and accept your defeat.

333
00:19:49,458 --> 00:19:51,750
Auhhh!

334
00:19:51,833 --> 00:19:53,583
[MUSUJIME] Ugh!

335
00:19:53,666 --> 00:19:57,833
[painful gasps]

336
00:19:59,208 --> 00:20:02,125
[glass breaking]

337
00:20:02,208 --> 00:20:06,333
[ACCELERATOR] True. My power
