338
00:20:06,416 --> 00:20:10,208
I may even need to step
down as this city's top dog.

339
00:20:11,541 --> 00:20:13,708
And yet, here I am.

340
00:20:15,208 --> 00:20:17,333
[ACCELERATOR] As long as the
kid's around, for some reason,

341
00:20:17,416 --> 00:20:21,708
I'm still determined
