347
00:20:33,291 --> 00:20:34,416
Yeah.

348
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,375
Hmmm?

349
00:20:35,458 --> 00:20:36,833
What, is something
the matter?

350
00:20:36,916 --> 00:20:39,083
Hah! At this point,
what isn't the matter?

351
00:20:39,916 --> 00:20:42,083
[KAMIJO] I came here to
see how Shirai was doing.

352
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:44,500
Errr!

353
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,125
[KAMIJO] Real bad idea.

