00:20:52,958 --> 00:20:55,083
[sighs] It's just my luck.

357
00:20:55,166 --> 00:20:56,583
[INDEX] So? What
about the object at

358
00:20:56,666 --> 00:20:58,125
the middle of this whole mess?

